            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1597.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Squeeze the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong> into a large bowl</p>\r\n<p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and mix to combine</p>\r\n<p>Wash, then add the <strong>baby leaf spinach</strong>&nbsp;to the bowl and give it a gentle mix up until coated in the <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
